   For more than three decades, Fernald produced uranium metal to support
   the U.S. Defense Program. complete story
   Truck Fernald will transport approximately 4 million cubic feet of
   nuclear material and low-level radioactive, hazardous and mixed waste
   by truck through closure. truck
   Rail By 2005, will transport approximately 626,000 tons of waste by
   rail to an off-site commercial disposal facility. rail
   Monthly Shipping Project and Shipment Progress Monthly Shipping
   Projection and Shipment Progress update
   Emergency Planning Once a truck or train leaves the Fernald site, DOE
   and Fluor Fernald have the ability to track a shipment through the
   carriers. emergency planning
